Expected Result: The enterd data should be displayed in the "First name" field

Test Step: 2.Enter second name in the "surname field"
Expected Result: The enterd data should be displayed in the "Surname" field

Test Step: 5.Select Date of Birth

Test Case Description: To validate facebook account creation functionality with field level validation of First name fiels
Pre-Condition: Launch brower with url "www.facebook.com" and navigate to account creation page
Test Step: Leave the "First name" field blank and move to the next field
Expected Result: The error message"First name field is mandatory" should be displayed

Test Step: Enter the alphabetic and numeric values in the "First name" field
Expected Result: The enterd data should be displayed in the "First name" field

Test Step: Enter the name with special character in the "First name" field
Expected Result: The error message "First name" field should not contain special characters other than "." and "_"

Test Step: Enter the name with special character in the "First name" field
Expected Result: The enterd data should be displayed in the "First name" field

Test Case Description: To validate facebook account creation functionality with field level validation of Date of Birth dropdown field
Pre-Condition: Launch brower with url "www.facebook.com" and navigate to account creation page
Test Step: 1.Enter the first name in the "First name" field
Expected Result: The enterd data should be displayed in the "Firstname" field

Test Step: 2.Enter the first name in the "Surname" field
Expected Result: The enterd data should be displayed in the "Surname" field

Test Step: 3.Verify all the dates are displayed in the date drop down field
Expected Result: The dates from 1 to 31 should be displayed

Test Step: 4.Verify all the months are displayed in the drop down field
Expected Result: The months from january to december should be displayed

Test Step: 5.Verify all the years are displayed in the drop down field
Expected Result: The years from 1905 to current year should be displayed
